                            <h2>Arts Faculty Launches Tech Lab</h2>
                            <ul class="highlights">
                                <li>
                                    <div class="mid-img">
                                        <a href="https://bulletin.hku.hk/teaching_learning/arts-faculty-launches-tech-lab/" target="_blank">
                                                                                            <img src="/file/blog/1548/ARTS ATLAB_Logo 2023_Standard Version_Full color_White BG png.png?w=160&amp;h=0&amp;proportional=1" alt="Arts Faculty Launches Tech Lab" />
                                                                                    </a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="details">
                                    <a href="https://bulletin.hku.hk/teaching_learning/arts-faculty-launches-tech-lab/" target="_blank">The potential of AI in arts and the humanities is in its early days, but the Faculty of Arts is at the frontline with the launch of its new Arts Tech Lab to support teaching on digital humanities and entrepreneurship and to promote AI in research...</a>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <span class="more"><a href="https://bulletin.hku.hk/teaching_learning/arts-faculty-launches-tech-lab/" target="_blank">MORE</a></span>
