                                                        <div class="inner-box">
                        <div class="inner-box-top"></div>
                        <div class="inner-box-middle">
                            <h2>The Convivium of the Faculty of Arts</h2>
                            <ul class="highlights">
                                <li>
                                    <div class="mid-img">
                                        <a href="https://convivium.arts.hku.hk/" target="_blank">
                                                                                            <img src="/file/blog/1548/Faculty of Arts_Convivium_logo 2023_trans FINAL 0904.png?w=160&amp;h=0&amp;proportional=1" alt="" />
                                                                                    </a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="details">
                                    <a href="https://convivium.arts.hku.hk/" target="_blank">The Convivium provides a place for professoriate researchers, postdoctoral fellows and postgraduate students to meet, and a context in which to discuss a variety of matters: from publishing strategies to teaching innovations to career networking and much more. </a>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
